-- Hong Kong Stocks Advance; Benchmark Hang Seng Index Rises for Seventh Day
-- Darren Boey
-- 2010-06-17T02:03:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/hong-kong-stocks-advance-benchmark-hang-seng-index-rises-for-seventh-day.html

          
          
             Hong Kong stocks rose, lifting the
Hang Seng Index higher for a seventh straight day. The Hang Seng
gained 0.6 percent to 20,186.69 as of 10:02 a.m. local time,
with five stocks advancing for each one that declined.  
          
          


  


        